<chapter id="relnotes:changelog" lang="en">
	<title>Changelog</title>

	<section id="relnotes:changelog:general">
		<title>General</title>
		<itemizedlist>
			<listitem>
				<simpara>
					Domain controller slaves are not registered as authoritative DNS servers for their DNS forward/reverse zones anymore. They are still valid DNS resolvers for clients. This greatly reduced the response size of queries for authoritative DNS servers (<u:bug>40139</u:bug>).
				</simpara>
			</listitem>
		</itemizedlist>
	</section>

	<section id="relnotes:changelog:import">
		<title>Import scripts</title>
		<itemizedlist>
			<listitem>
				<simpara>
					A new check script
					<filename>/usr/share/ucs-school-import/scripts/ucs-school-verify-class-memberships</filename> has
					been added to the package <package>ucs-school-import</package>. It verifies that the the class group membership of the LDAP objects matches
					with a specified CSV file. The script performs a read-only check and does not alter any LDAP data (<u:bug>40215</u:bug>).
				</simpara>
			</listitem>
		</itemizedlist>
	</section>

