			<title>LDAP ACL changes</title>
			<itemizedlist>
				<listitem>
					<simpara>
						LDAP ACLs are now installed domain wide using the LDAP ACL extension mechanism. Backup domaincontrollers will now use the registered ACLs without having the UCS@school app installed (<u:bug>40123</u:bug>).
					</simpara>
				</listitem>
			</itemizedlist>
		</section>
